N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 582.11 - Vehicle and traffic law applicable to cases not covered

State Regulations

In all cases not specifically covered by this Part, the
provisions of the Vehicle and Traffic Law of the State of New York shall
apply. Notes
